        About this item

        • WIPE-FRIENDLY SYNTHETIC LEATHER - The womens white sneakers, made of soft synthetic leather, are water-resistant and easy to wipe clean with a long-lasting design. They are also designed with adjustable lace-up for a customized fit.
        • SOFT & COMFORTABLE - These women's white tennis shoes provide a luxuriously comfortable and soft wearing experience, showcasing meticulously crafted features such as padded memory foam and a plush collar. Rest assured, walking in them is a truly comfortable endeavor.
        • NON-SLIP OUTSOLE - Crafted with white PU leather sneakers, these women's sneakers boast sturdy yet flexible synthetic rubber outsoles, featuring a specially textured bottom for enhanced grip and friction. These shoes provide slip resistance, ensuring stability even in wet weather conditions.
        • SHOES WITH DIVERSE OUTFITS - These womens casual shoes work well with both modern and retro outfits. They look super cute when paired with shorts, pants, skirts, or dressesan absolute must-have in your closet.
        • VERSATILE - Adokoo women's fashoin sneakers are suitable for a range of occasions, from casual outings to everyday activities. Their comfort and style make them a go-to choice for leisurely strolls, daily errands, and laid-back outdoor gatherings, embodying a exemplary blend of fashion and functionality.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        Learn more how customers reviews work on Amazon
